was flying the plane?

06:18.200 --> 06:22.210
Logan's one of the first airports
with the pearl autopilot system.

06:22.220 --> 06:24.640
Plane landed itself right on time.

06:24.650 --> 06:27.020
Unlike every flight I've ever taken.

06:27.030 --> 06:31.220
well,let me assure you we'd be
