07:21.540 --> 07:24.740
D.C.Has sent me here to
make sure we get results.

07:24.760 --> 07:28.820
Standard level four hazmat
suits are required to go in.

07:28.830 --> 07:33.400
Members from each agency on
the starting line as follows.

07:33.410 --> 07:36.370
Cia,baronoff.

07:36.380 --> 07:40.160
Fbi,charlie francis and john scott.

07:40.170 --> 07:42.900
Everyone else stand by.

07:42.910 --> 07:45.370
Okay,people,let's move.

07:46.270 --> 07:47.220
Sir!

07:47.230 --> 07:49.990
Olivia dunham,fbi interagency liaison.

07:50.000 --> 07:53.550
Liaison on an interagency
task force. Gotta love that.

07:53.880 --> 07:56.680
Kind of like powdered
sugar on a glazed donut.

07:56.690 --> 08:01.380
Excuse me,if I'm gonna do my job
effectively,I like my information first-hand.

08:01.390 --> 08:04.590
That's not redundancy.
That's accountability.

08:05.700 --> 08:09.380
I know exactly who you are.

08:09.390 --> 08:12.390
You want in,liaison?

08:12.400 --> 08:14.480
Suit up.

08:56.560 --> 08:59.090
What kind of terrorism is this?

08:59.100 --> 09:01.660
Who says it's terrorism?

